类 WrappingJavaFileManager<M extends javax.tools.JavaFileManager>

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.tools.ForwardingJavaFileManager<M>
      • javac.api.WrappingJavaFileManager<M>
  • 类型参数:
    M - the type of file manager wrapped to by this object
    所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Closeable, java.io.Flushable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, javax.tools.JavaFileManager, javax.tools.OptionChecker

    public class WrappingJavaFileManager<M extends javax.tools.JavaFileManager>
extends javax.tools.ForwardingJavaFileManager<M>
    Wraps all calls to a given file manager. Subclasses of this class might override some of these methods and might also provide additional fields and methods.

    This class might be moved to javax.tools in a future release.

    This is NOT part of any supported API. If you write code that depends on this, you do so at your own risk. This code and its internal interfaces are subject to change or deletion without notice.

    从以下版本开始:
    1.6
    作者:
    Peter von der Ahé
